metadata.name: Enlightened Journey #191
metadata.description:
A digital journey through nature.

Made in p5js

Special thanks to @Zancan and @TenebrisVia for inspiring me to code with nature, along with the work of Linda Rous for inspiring the use of perspective and stairs in the scene. Also, thanks to the FX Hash and Twitter communities for the wonderful feedback and suggestions which helped throughout the design process.

metadata.name: Imperfect #79
metadata.description:
Inspired by nail and thread art, I explored the possibilities in generated art. Instead of perfectly symmetrical patterns I was attracted to the imperfect ones. It resulted in endless interesting patterns and shapes so I decided that this will be my first edition of 500 pieces.

I made a light edition as well, holders will be able to mint this one for free (tba)

Press e in live mode for a 2000x2000 download

Download a higher resolution by adding to the URL:
&density=2 (4000x4000)
&density=3 (6000x6000)

Lammetje june 2022

metadata.name: BlockonBlock #136
metadata.description:
‘BlockonBlock’ is the precursor and reserve pass for the upcoming ‘Hashway ‘69 Revisited’ collection by pixelwank. 
Free mint for pixelwank holders on tezos - After 3 days any remainders will be opened up to the public for 2tez.  

‘BlockonBlock’ was a study of rectangles following on from the use of circles in Generacci. 
Placements & building sizes are based on numbers from the fibonacci sequence. 

I had a blast making these and I hope they bring the collector as much enjoyment.

'Hashway '69 Revisited' coming soon :)

23 colour palettes 
14 colour overlays 
21% chance of extra lines
Click the image or press ‘s’ or ‘S’ in live move to save a 3000x3000 png 

Thanks for collectin’ & shoutouts to Circolors for the support <3 

R.I.F.F. 
Remember it’s for fun
